[
  {
    "startTime": 2.1,
    "endTime": 3.766,
    "text": "Coming."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.0,
    "endTime": 5.166,
    "text": "Good afternoon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.2,
    "endTime": 6.766,
    "text": "-I am Olaf. -Hey, Olaf."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.0,
    "endTime": 9.166,
    "text": "Please let me finish, and I like warm hugs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.2,
    "endTime": 11.2,
    "text": "This is my associate, Sven."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.233,
    "endTime": 13.733,
    "text": "We're going door to door looking for family traditions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.766,
    "endTime": 16.233,
    "text": "Tell us yours, and we'll decide if it's special enough."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.265,
    "endTime": 18.5,
    "text": "Oh, we make candy canes together."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.5,
    "endTime": 20.166,
    "text": "Ooh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.533,
    "endTime": 22.666,
    "text": "Sugar rush."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.7,
    "endTime": 24.2,
    "text": "You're supposed to eat it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.233,
    "endTime": 27.566000000000003,
    "text": "Eat my new nose? Why would I do that?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.6,
    "endTime": 30.233,
    "text": "Because it's that time of year."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.266,
    "endTime": 34.132,
    "text": "Hmm. It's that time of year."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.566,
    "endTime": 46.6,
    "text": "♪ Happy merry, holly jolly ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.633,
    "endTime": 48.233000000000004,
    "text": "♪ Seasons greetings here ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.266,
    "endTime": 52.466,
    "text": "♪ I'm wondering what your family does at that time of year  ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.5,
    "endTime": 56.0,
    "text": "♪ Love and joy and peace on Earth and tidings of good cheer ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.033,
    "endTime": 60.0,
    "text": "♪ Do you have tradition things for that time of year? ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.0,
    "endTime": 64.099,
    "text": "♪ Well, we hang up boughs of evergreen on every single doorway ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.132,
    "endTime": 68.033,
    "text": "♪ Bake a giant cookie in the wavy shape of Norway ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.066,
    "endTime": 69.566,
    "text": "♪ Go from door to door to door to door while sailing with our choir"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.733,
    "endTime": 76.766,
    "text": "♪ Hang up all your giant socks above an open fire ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 77.0,
    "endTime": 79.166,
    "text": "That sounds safe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.2,
    "endTime": 81.2,
    "text": "♪ So happy merry Yuletide carol ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.233,
    "endTime": 83.16600000000001,
    "text": "♪ Faithful friends are \"deer\" ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.2,
    "endTime": 88.033,
    "text": "♪ Thanks for sharing what you do at that time of year  ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.066,
    "endTime": 92.13300000000001,
    "text": "We better get a move on if we're gonna hit every house in the kingdom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.533,
    "endTime": 95.5,
    "text": "♪ Jolly merry, happy holly ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.533,
    "endTime": 97.133,
    "text": "♪ On a midnight clear ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.166,
    "endTime": 100.5,
    "text": "♪ I'm here to ask you what you do  at that time of year ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.5,
    "endTime": 102.633,
    "text": "Hi! Shalom! Happy solstice!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.666,
    "endTime": 104.2,
    "text": "Fancy chandelier."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.233,
    "endTime": 108.033,
    "text": "♪ I'm looking for tradition stuff for that time of year ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.066,
    "endTime": 111.265,
    "text": "♪ Well, we make our decorations out of flotsam and jetsam ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.5,
    "endTime": 113.0,
    "text": "♪ Bake a yummy fruitcake and you can't leave till you get some ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.533,
    "endTime": 117.0,
    "text": "That went right through me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.033,
    "endTime": 120.3,
    "text": "♪ Buy each other presents and then hide them very nimbly ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.3,
    "endTime": 124.133,
    "text": "♪ Wait up for a chubby man to shimmy down your chimney ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.166,
    "endTime": 126.7,
    "text": "Breaking and entering - okay on Christmas."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.733,
    "endTime": 129.233,
    "text": "♪ Oh, happy merry, mule-tied barrels ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.265,
    "endTime": 130.666,
    "text": "♪ Faithful, gladsome cheer ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.699,
    "endTime": 136.33300000000003,
    "text": "♪ Thanks for sharing what you do at that time of year ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.366,
    "endTime": 138.16600000000003,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.2,
    "endTime": 141.63299999999998,
    "text": "♪ We knit scarves and sweaters, and we wear our matching mittens ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.666,
    "endTime": 145.033,
    "text": "♪ Don't forget the jammies that I knitted for my kittens ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.066,
    "endTime": 149.166,
    "text": "♪ Eight nights in a row we light menorahs on our mantels ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.2,
    "endTime": 155.29899999999998,
    "text": "You cut down a tree, and then you dress its corpse with candles."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.366,
    "endTime": 160.5,
    "text": "I love it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.7,
    "endTime": 166.13199999999998,
    "text": "♪ Anna and Elsa ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.166,
    "endTime": 170.333,
    "text": "♪ Will have all that they need ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.366,
    "endTime": 175.632,
    "text": "♪ I'll fill my sleigh here with the help of my steed ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.666,
    "endTime": 178.766,
    "text": "♪ It'll be the best time of year ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.0,
    "endTime": 182.333,
    "text": "♪ It's up to you ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.366,
    "endTime": 183.76600000000002,
    "text": "♪ Up to me ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.0,
    "endTime": 185.566,
    "text": "♪ Me ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.0,
    "endTime": 185.566,
    "text": "♪ Me ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.6,
    "endTime": 186.632,
    "text": "♪ Up to ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.666,
    "endTime": 187.666,
    "text": "Meow!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.4,
    "endTime": 193.166,
    "text": "♪ Oh, happy merry, Mele Kaliki ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.2,
    "endTime": 195.666,
    "text": "♪ Holly jolly, happy tappy ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.7,
    "endTime": 197.766,
    "text": "♪ Chubby man will soon appear ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.0,
    "endTime": 200.066,
    "text": "♪ And faithful friends are tiny deer ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.1,
    "endTime": 202.033,
    "text": "♪ And festive tidings, midnight clear ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.066,
    "endTime": 204.233,
    "text": "And can I leave this fruitcake here?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.266,
    "endTime": 210.6,
    "text": "♪ At that time of year ♪"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.633,
    "endTime": 211.633,
    "text": "Meow!"
  }
]